    <div class="row align-items-center mb-5 flex-md-row-reverse">
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <div class="career-image bg-light"
                style="height: 800px; background: url('/assets/placetogrow.png') center/cover no-repeat;"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-6">
            <h3 class="fw-semibold f-size">A Place to Grow</h3>
            <p class="text-muted why-us">From your first day to your next promotion, we’re committed to helping you
                reach your
                potential.
                At STAGGER, growth is more than a promise — it’s part of your everyday experience. We invest in your
                ambitions with tailored development paths, cross-functional projects, and a culture that celebrates
                curiosity. Whether you're switching roles, stepping into leadership, or mastering your craft, you'll be
                supported by mentors, training, and a community that wants to see you thrive.

            </p>
        </div>
